Upload a single image using node.js

For single picture upload
1.Click "choose file" button, then select the image that you want to upload. 
2.Click "Submit" to confirm upload, then the webpage will show a http link. 
3.Click the link to access the image that you just uploaded.

For zip with multiple pictures upload
1.Click "choose file" button, then select the zip file.
2.Click "Submit" to confirm, then webpage will jump to another page automatically.
3.In the new page, URLs of pictures in the zip will be shown.
4.Click the URLs, the picture will be open in browser.

The first version is finished. And All the tasks required of the quiz is done.
